{"tid":1693290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（抵制TVB）茲曼尼傢俬 支那貨扮高檔嘢 狂落CCTVB廣告！","createTime":"2019-11-04T13:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T23:30:48.000Z","uid":75759,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"537f652c30bb275cd32ded160d0ca088922ea375","tid":1693290,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:49:40.000Z","msg":"各位marketing JJ注意，<br />\nTVB係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>品牌負資產</strong></span></span>，喺TVB落廣告，<br />\n你哋苦心經營嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">品牌形象將付諸流水</span></span></strong>！無人可憐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTVB今個月開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約，Keep住個氣勢到年底啦！<br />\n廣告界多番強調，去FB洗版係有用ga<br />\n<br />\n是晚重溫@4 Nov 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">茲曼尼</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Giormanisofa/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGiormanisofa%2F&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=fac0e71c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Giormanisofa/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kPo6V8Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkPo6V8Z.jpg&h=e0cd3e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【茲曼尼做咩？】<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">支那貨色扮高檔</span></strong></span><br />\n近年港人北上消費成風，大量廉價家具充斥中港市場，但茲曼尼董事兼總設計師吳紹棠認為，香港消費者向來精明，購買耐用品如沙發及家具，會講求品質及售後服務，因此不擔心內地家具商可以搶走港客，「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>內地家具市場經常鬥平，以低成本製作，表面看似高檔的沙發，內裏的海棉密度、母架結構及安全標準可能不符合理想</strong></span>，雖然只賣千多元，但並不耐用，計起來比售價五六千元，但用足六七年的產品更不划算。」<br />\n<br />\n吳紹棠坦言，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>茲曼尼成立初期，以製造中下檔次產品為主，近年覷準消費者對家具設計及用料的要求愈來愈高，於是轉走中高檔路線</strong></span>，近年更與意大利及德國等地設計師合作，將最新的沙發潮流及設計意念帶進香港。「以前買沙發只求實用，現時還要追求美觀及多功能，舉例香港的家居面積狹窄，部份客廳呈方形，沙發與電視之間的空間，往往被浪費了，所以近年我們設計不少L形沙發，變相多一個座位，亦可令家居擺設看來更多元化。」<br />\n<br />\n        他又指，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>茲曼尼對產品質量十分重視，內地廠房雖然只有六七百名員工，但卻參照了歐洲的生產模式運作</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，「因為製造沙發的加工程序，九成由人手來做，稍有差池都會影響產品質素，即使是車歪了一條線，測檢員也不會蓋章讓沙發出廠。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.hkhl.hk/dailynews/headline_news_detail_columnist.asp?id=98274&amp;section_name=wtt&amp;kw=78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.hkhl.hk%2Fdailynews%2Fheadline_news_detail_columnist.asp%3Fid%3D98274%26section_name%3Dwtt%26kw%3D78&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=c23c3dd3\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.hkhl.hk/dailynews/headline_news_detail_columnist.asp?id=98274&amp;section_name=wtt&amp;kw=78</a><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再唔撤budget，業績定仆直！盡快同TVB割席！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【抵制CCTVB 任務流程】<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請用幾秒去派嬲、留言、推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n※請善用template，清晰表達訴求<br />\n無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FQU9TX7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFQU9TX7.jpg&h=395b21d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/FQU9TX7.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFQU9TX7.jpg&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=9069ac5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/FQU9TX7.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n記得bookmark: TVB廣告客戶名單！！ <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=8e5a89eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a> <br />\n－－－－－－－ <br />\n請即follow: <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=b7e03a52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb<br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=b9fb0a60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝大家</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9576a1fb0e11030e306b4d53e5c47695602944b0","tid":1693290,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a08008188ce64fff4ba5cda28a98e3a0cde2e00","tid":1693290,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287db82bcd4fd441b40a7a657b15e56168e48221","tid":1693290,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:50:52.000Z","